WEBVTT

01:11.360 --> 01:12.080
I like you.

02:47.880 --> 02:48.880
See you tomorrow.

02:53.600 --> 02:54.600
See you tomorrow.

04:10.520 --> 04:12.450
So he didn't say anything that day.

04:14.200 --> 04:16.000
I'm not sure if he heard me.

04:16.640 --> 04:18.000
Because he didn't say anything

04:18.000 --> 04:19.200
and just took me home.

04:21.079 --> 04:21.610
Xiaocen.

04:22.000 --> 04:23.000
You're amazing.

04:23.800 --> 04:25.260
You just said it like that.

04:25.800 --> 04:28.000
Didn't you tell me to be more proactive?

04:28.240 --> 04:29.500
Alright, don't worry.

04:30.080 --> 04:32.200
Xu Xiao might just be hesitating.

04:33.040 --> 04:34.370
Hesitating about what?

04:35.360 --> 04:36.400
I mean,

04:37.120 --> 04:38.520
he's just processing it.

04:41.720 --> 04:43.360
I really don't know what to do.

04:43.360 --> 04:44.760
It's fine, Xiaocen.

04:44.920 --> 04:45.600
Let me tell you.

04:45.600 --> 04:46.800
If I were Xu Xiao,

04:46.800 --> 04:49.600
I would have definitely said yes to you that night.

04:51.600 --> 04:52.600
Is it possible

04:52.600 --> 04:53.930
that he didn't hear you?

04:54.480 --> 04:55.880
If he didn't hear you,

04:56.120 --> 04:57.200
just say it again.

04:57.400 --> 04:59.040
Since you've already said it once,

04:59.040 --> 05:01.100
saying it a hundred times is the same.

05:01.480 --> 05:02.810
I'm not saying it again.

05:02.920 --> 05:03.400
Come on.

05:03.680 --> 05:04.680
Look into my eyes.

05:05.360 --> 05:05.820
Xu Xiao,

05:06.200 --> 05:07.040
I like you.

05:08.680 --> 05:10.120
Yuexin.

05:10.240 --> 05:11.480
You can do it, Xiaocen.

05:11.480 --> 05:12.600
I can't.

05:12.800 --> 05:13.680
You can.

05:19.200 --> 05:20.680
Um, Zhuoting,

05:21.600 --> 05:22.930
can I ask you something?

05:23.200 --> 05:23.730
Go ahead.

05:24.360 --> 05:26.220
When you and Xiaoyi got together,

05:26.520 --> 05:27.720
did you confess first,

05:27.720 --> 05:28.720
or did she?

05:29.080 --> 05:30.320
Of course I did.

05:30.440 --> 05:32.700
How could I let a girl make the first move?

05:34.560 --> 05:36.520
Why the sudden question?

05:39.800 --> 05:40.280
If...

05:40.480 --> 05:41.880
I mean, hypothetically,

05:42.720 --> 05:44.180
if Xiaoyi confessed to you

05:44.640 --> 05:46.700
and you didn't respond immediately,

05:46.880 --> 05:47.800
what would happen?

05:47.800 --> 05:49.460
Then we'd definitely be over.

05:49.520 --> 05:51.520
If I didn't give her a direct answer,

05:52.000 --> 05:53.530
she would probably hate me.

05:55.440 --> 05:55.880
Xu...

05:55.880 --> 05:56.560
Xu Xiao.

05:57.520 --> 05:59.120
Why are you suddenly asking me

05:59.120 --> 06:00.520
such a private question?

06:01.400 --> 06:02.130
Just asking.

06:05.360 --> 06:06.880
Is there something going on with you?

06:06.880 --> 06:07.320
No.

06:07.640 --> 06:08.840
Don't talk nonsense.

06:09.360 --> 06:10.600
Does it have to do with Zhao Xiaocen?

06:10.600 --> 06:11.040
No.

06:16.640 --> 06:17.700
One more question.

06:18.920 --> 06:19.520
Do you and Xiaoyi

06:19.520 --> 06:21.840
usually go anywhere romantic?

06:23.000 --> 06:26.000
We usually just walk around the market

06:26.280 --> 06:28.000
and grab a bite to eat or something.

06:28.000 --> 06:28.600
Oh, right.

06:28.840 --> 06:29.920
There's a music bar

06:30.360 --> 06:31.760
that's really romantic.

06:33.280 --> 06:34.409
Send me the address.

06:36.360 --> 06:38.159
I knew something was up with you.

06:38.280 --> 06:40.140
You have to tell me what it's about

06:40.320 --> 06:41.400
before I tell you.

06:47.480 --> 06:49.159
I solemnly request

06:49.760 --> 06:51.360
that you send me the address.

07:07.400 --> 07:08.260
I sent it to you.

07:10.480 --> 07:11.000
Thanks.

07:11.720 --> 07:12.650
I'm leaving now.

07:17.560 --> 07:18.490
I've scanned it.

07:18.520 --> 07:19.120
Thank you.

07:42.880 --> 07:43.740
Do you have time

07:45.520 --> 07:46.159
tonight?

07:48.040 --> 07:48.800
Yes.

07:49.680 --> 07:51.210
I'll send you the location.

07:52.280 --> 07:52.840
Okay.

08:23.200 --> 08:24.880
I'm an hour early.

08:26.840 --> 08:28.040
So early.

08:36.600 --> 08:37.159
Hello.

08:37.559 --> 08:38.080
Hello.

08:40.400 --> 08:41.520
Can I help you?

08:41.880 --> 08:43.559
Excuse me, where is seat three?

08:43.559 --> 08:44.360
It's this way.

08:45.000 --> 08:45.800
Okay, thanks.

08:45.880 --> 08:46.810
You're welcome.

09:23.000 --> 09:23.440
Hello?

09:23.920 --> 09:24.560
Hello?

09:25.640 --> 09:26.440
Where are you?

09:28.560 --> 09:30.480
Isn't it at eight? I'm at home.

09:32.920 --> 09:33.920
I was just asking.

09:35.720 --> 09:36.780
It's fine. No rush.

09:37.680 --> 09:38.600
That shop

09:38.920 --> 09:40.050
is a bit hard to find.

09:40.600 --> 09:42.160
I haven't left yet anyway.

09:43.320 --> 09:44.120
Where are you?

09:45.080 --> 09:46.410
I'm at the antique shop.

09:47.400 --> 09:48.660
I'll head over in a bit.

09:49.240 --> 09:49.760
Okay.

09:51.680 --> 09:53.400
See you in a bit then.

09:53.880 --> 09:54.680
See you later.

11:01.320 --> 11:01.720
Hello.

11:02.040 --> 11:02.680
Hello?

11:03.560 --> 11:04.360
Where are you?

11:05.200 --> 11:06.000
I'm almost there.

11:06.000 --> 11:06.800
I'm at that...

11:08.080 --> 11:10.520
I'm outside that white coffee shop.

11:10.600 --> 11:11.730
I'll be right there.

11:12.120 --> 11:13.250
I know where you are.

11:13.400 --> 11:14.330
I'll come to you.

11:14.960 --> 11:15.760
Wait a moment.

11:39.920 --> 11:40.240
I,

11:40.640 --> 11:41.560
I've arrived.

11:42.360 --> 11:43.160
Where are you?

11:43.360 --> 11:43.960
Here.

11:44.360 --> 11:45.020
Right here.

11:45.120 --> 11:45.800
I'm here.

11:49.960 --> 11:50.820
I just got here.

11:52.160 --> 11:53.690
How long have you been here?

11:55.960 --> 11:57.020
I just got here too.

12:00.200 --> 12:01.130
It's over there.

12:01.160 --> 12:01.690
Let's go.

12:01.720 --> 12:02.360
Okay.

12:17.480 --> 12:18.880
It's pretty good, right?

12:19.280 --> 12:19.680
Here.

12:33.680 --> 12:34.640
It sounds nice.

12:37.440 --> 12:37.920
Okay.

12:39.000 --> 12:39.440
Hello.

12:39.760 --> 12:40.160
Hello.

12:40.640 --> 12:41.360
Here are your drinks.

12:41.360 --> 12:41.960
Thank you.

12:43.320 --> 12:44.450
That's everything.

13:30.520 --> 13:32.120
Actually, when I was little,

13:33.920 --> 13:35.650
right after my dad's accident,

13:37.840 --> 13:39.200
for a very long time,

13:40.560 --> 13:41.890
I became very negative.

13:43.760 --> 13:45.560
Because many kids in my class...

13:46.320 --> 13:49.180
We're all kids from Jingdezhen ceramics families.

13:50.520 --> 13:51.320
Their parents

13:52.440 --> 13:54.640
would deliberately make them avoid me.

13:57.200 --> 13:57.800
My dad

13:58.920 --> 14:01.050
didn't want to see his friends either.

14:02.680 --> 14:04.210
So every time after school,

14:05.560 --> 14:08.090
I had to wait at the school gate for a long time.

14:09.960 --> 14:11.360
I waited until those kids

14:11.920 --> 14:13.720
were picked up by their parents.

14:14.640 --> 14:16.400
Only then would my dad show up to pick me up.

14:16.400 --> 14:16.800
Xiao,

14:17.320 --> 14:18.850
Daddy's here to pick you up.

14:21.440 --> 14:21.840
Xiao.

14:30.000 --> 14:30.960
Since then,

14:32.920 --> 14:34.580
I've been used to being alone,

14:36.200 --> 14:38.000
and doing everything by myself.

14:39.680 --> 14:41.200
I'm used to expecting the worst

14:41.200 --> 14:42.600
in everything.

14:45.320 --> 14:46.720
So no matter the outcome,

14:50.480 --> 14:52.280
I wouldn't be too disappointed.

14:55.680 --> 14:57.080
What you said last night,

14:58.600 --> 14:59.200
I heard it.

15:06.840 --> 15:08.040
I didn't dare to think

15:09.680 --> 15:12.010
such a wonderful thing would happen to me.

15:16.480 --> 15:17.410
I didn't believe

15:19.200 --> 15:21.800
the person I care about would care about me too.

15:33.360 --> 15:35.490
But this time, I don't want to run away.

15:36.880 --> 15:38.010
I want to be like you,

15:39.560 --> 15:40.760
and be brave for once.

15:47.720 --> 15:48.320
Xiaocen.

15:51.080 --> 15:51.800
I like you.

17:21.040 --> 17:21.880
We

17:22.960 --> 17:24.160
are together now.

17:47.080 --> 17:47.720
Xu Xiao.

17:48.080 --> 17:49.040
What are these?

17:49.600 --> 17:50.240
These

17:50.760 --> 17:51.920
were from former JCU seniors

17:51.920 --> 17:52.850
who told me about

17:53.080 --> 17:54.740
this custom they left behind.

17:55.320 --> 17:57.040
People hang what they want to say

17:57.040 --> 17:58.680
and the things they want to leave behind

17:58.680 --> 17:59.480
on the tree.

18:04.960 --> 18:07.020
When I was little, I never understood

18:07.040 --> 18:07.880
why my parents

18:07.880 --> 18:09.610
always made me clean the house.

18:10.120 --> 18:11.640
It turns out that when the house is messy,

18:11.640 --> 18:13.240
your mind is truly messy too.

18:15.960 --> 18:17.020
What did you write?

18:18.080 --> 18:20.240
I bit my nails off

18:20.440 --> 18:22.170
and want to get them done again.

18:56.840 --> 18:57.570
What is this?

18:58.880 --> 18:59.680
A leaf.

19:02.640 --> 19:04.570
A butterfly. It feels so familiar,

19:05.000 --> 19:05.860
yet so distant.

19:06.800 --> 19:09.000
This is the moment I drew.

19:09.560 --> 19:11.040
Do you recognize it?

19:23.160 --> 19:24.890
Have you ever thought about it?

19:25.120 --> 19:26.720
If you could leave a sentence

19:27.040 --> 19:28.080
or an item behind,

19:29.280 --> 19:30.480
what would you leave?

19:35.800 --> 19:38.000
I don't think I've thought about it yet.

19:40.640 --> 19:41.680
But I believe

19:42.560 --> 19:43.620
what I leave behind

19:44.560 --> 19:47.220
will definitely be the most worthwhile things.

19:55.480 --> 19:57.560
Jing and the others are live streaming,

19:57.560 --> 19:59.420
setting up a stall at Taoxichuan.

19:59.560 --> 20:01.820
Look, there are more people than before.

20:02.120 --> 20:03.480
Xiaocen, look at this.

20:07.920 --> 20:08.600
Xu Xiao.

20:09.040 --> 20:10.080
What a coincidence.

20:10.080 --> 20:11.400
You guys are shopping too?

20:11.400 --> 20:11.800
Yeah.

20:12.120 --> 20:13.450
Are you shopping alone?

20:15.400 --> 20:15.840
Alone.

20:16.560 --> 20:17.960
Sometimes I come alone.

20:22.640 --> 20:23.700
Women's clothing.

20:24.840 --> 20:25.400
Just looking at clothes.

20:25.400 --> 20:26.160
Xu Xiao.

20:26.560 --> 20:27.560
Actually, the boys in our class

20:27.560 --> 20:29.160
all want to hang out with you.

20:29.400 --> 20:31.520
You don't have to be alone all the time.

20:31.520 --> 20:32.520
Alright, Xiaoyi.

20:32.640 --> 20:34.040
Let's not disturb Xu Xiao

20:34.360 --> 20:35.560
while he looks at clothes alone.

20:35.560 --> 20:36.090
Let's go.

20:36.720 --> 20:37.440
Bye.

20:49.120 --> 20:50.120
Sorry.

20:50.400 --> 20:52.330
Actually, you didn't have to hide.

20:53.760 --> 20:54.960
It's just that

20:55.640 --> 20:57.880
I don't really know how to face them

20:57.880 --> 20:58.600
if they found out.

20:58.600 --> 20:59.200
It's fine.

20:59.640 --> 21:00.100
I get it.

21:02.960 --> 21:03.490
Let's go.

21:25.840 --> 21:27.120
Mom, I'm not eating.

21:27.120 --> 21:28.280
My classmate is waiting for me.

21:28.280 --> 21:29.080
Wait a minute.

21:29.120 --> 21:31.000
Didn't you say you wanted rice noodles yesterday?

21:31.000 --> 21:32.640
Mom bought it for you early in the morning.

21:32.640 --> 21:33.720
I made plans with my classmates.

21:33.720 --> 21:34.760
We are having a big pizza today.

21:34.760 --> 21:35.490
I'm leaving.

21:38.320 --> 21:39.200
Slow down.

21:40.200 --> 21:41.440
Auntie.

21:42.440 --> 21:43.120
I want some.

21:43.600 --> 21:44.400
Come quickly.

21:50.440 --> 21:51.360
Taste it and see if you like it.

21:51.360 --> 21:51.680
Okay.

21:51.680 --> 21:53.140
Put down your chopsticks.

21:55.960 --> 21:58.600
Have your millet porridge. It's good for your stomach.

21:58.600 --> 22:00.680
Look at this, too much oil and chili.

22:00.680 --> 22:01.760
Your stomach can't handle it,

22:01.760 --> 22:02.820
so you can't eat it.

22:05.000 --> 22:05.920
Sis.

22:06.200 --> 22:08.720
Aren't you tired of millet porridge every day?

22:08.720 --> 22:10.560
What's wrong with having a taste occasionally?

22:10.560 --> 22:11.040
Here.

22:11.280 --> 22:12.440
This is Jiangxi.

22:12.640 --> 22:14.160
She finally got into a university here.

22:14.160 --> 22:15.000
She should experience

22:15.000 --> 22:16.330
the local food and life.

22:18.600 --> 22:19.600
Let me tell you,

22:19.680 --> 22:21.520
of course we have to watch what she eats.

22:21.520 --> 22:22.600
You spoil Xing.

22:22.920 --> 22:23.400
Look at her.

22:23.400 --> 22:24.160
One day she wants this,

22:24.160 --> 22:24.840
the next day she wants that.

22:24.840 --> 22:26.000
Pizzas, hamburgers.

22:26.000 --> 22:27.040
They're so unnutritious.

22:27.040 --> 22:28.520
You really can't raise a child like this.

22:28.520 --> 22:30.080
You can't get better.

22:30.840 --> 22:32.480
Don't waste this. I'll eat it for lunch.

22:32.480 --> 22:33.720
Sister, let me eat it.

22:34.320 --> 22:35.320
No need.

22:35.320 --> 22:36.400
I'll eat it.

22:43.240 --> 22:45.370
Mom, I'm going to be late. I'm leaving.

22:47.160 --> 22:48.760
You finished eating so fast.

22:48.840 --> 22:49.720
Wait a minute.

22:50.360 --> 22:51.160
Wait a minute.

22:51.520 --> 22:52.080
Cup.

22:52.520 --> 22:52.920
Here.

22:53.880 --> 22:55.040
Alright, it's packed.

22:55.040 --> 22:57.040
Remember to drink water, it's too hot.

22:57.040 --> 22:57.920
Be careful of the heat.

22:57.920 --> 22:58.760
Got it.

23:11.240 --> 23:12.640
I brought you breakfast.

23:14.360 --> 23:14.960
Jiaoziba.

23:16.000 --> 23:16.640
Thank you.

23:17.160 --> 23:18.690
I didn't know what you like,

23:19.080 --> 23:20.680
so I just grabbed something.

23:20.960 --> 23:21.820
You can tell me.

23:22.360 --> 23:24.400
I can bring you what you like next time.

23:24.400 --> 23:25.480
Actually,

23:25.960 --> 23:27.560
I haven't eaten out much.

23:28.160 --> 23:29.620
My mom always cooks for me.

23:31.880 --> 23:33.540
Your mom is really nice to you.

23:34.600 --> 23:35.130
Let's go.

23:37.840 --> 23:38.900
Where is this from?

23:39.120 --> 23:40.650
I think it's called Li Dafu.

23:49.200 --> 23:51.240
Regarding the re-firing of ancient kilns,

23:51.240 --> 23:52.920
some have raised objections.

23:53.080 --> 23:54.800
They say that modern new kilns,

23:54.800 --> 23:56.160
both in terms of equipment

23:56.160 --> 23:57.400
and technology,

23:57.400 --> 23:58.560
are excellent.

23:58.680 --> 23:59.720
Why must we

24:00.080 --> 24:01.520
invest so much money

24:01.960 --> 24:03.920
to re-fire these ancient porcelain kilns?

24:03.920 --> 24:05.320
If we are particularly nostalgic,

24:05.320 --> 24:06.580
can't we build a new one

24:06.680 --> 24:08.280
according to the blueprints

24:08.760 --> 24:10.690
of these ancient porcelain kilns?

24:10.840 --> 24:13.300
It doesn't seem to be such a simple question.

24:13.840 --> 24:14.600
Who can say

24:14.920 --> 24:16.840
why we should re-fire ancient kilns?

24:16.840 --> 24:18.360
What is its significance?

24:19.000 --> 24:20.800
To create a tourist attraction.

24:21.080 --> 24:22.720
You have a head for business.

24:22.960 --> 24:24.800
Re-firing is a living inheritance.

24:24.800 --> 24:27.200
Jingdezhen must pass on this kiln fire.

24:28.320 --> 24:29.380
That is one reason.

24:31.200 --> 24:32.130
This afternoon,

24:32.760 --> 24:36.240
I will take the students to visit Weijiayao.

24:36.480 --> 24:38.560
We will have a field study there.

24:40.160 --> 24:41.280
Going to Weijiayao this afternoon.

24:41.280 --> 24:43.140
Does it mean we can go for a picnic?

24:43.400 --> 24:44.080
These ancient kilns

24:44.080 --> 24:46.480
are all built in places with beautiful scenery.

24:46.480 --> 24:47.920
No wonder the masters in ancient times

24:47.920 --> 24:49.720
knew how to choose good locations.

24:49.720 --> 24:51.040
Should we prepare some

24:51.080 --> 24:51.960
snacks?

24:52.280 --> 24:54.440
We need to combine learning and entertainment.

24:54.440 --> 24:55.100
Lin Yuexin.

24:55.360 --> 24:56.840
Let's have lunch together.

24:56.840 --> 24:58.040
We will go to the convenience store later

24:58.040 --> 24:59.360
to buy some snacks.

24:59.600 --> 25:00.760
See what you want to buy.

25:00.760 --> 25:01.440
It's rare for you to be so thoughtful.

25:01.440 --> 25:02.240
Is your stomach feeling better?

25:02.240 --> 25:02.960
Of course.

25:03.760 --> 25:05.600
Is Weijiayao near Hanxi Village?

25:05.600 --> 25:06.960
I heard it's very beautiful there,

25:06.960 --> 25:08.490
with large areas of forest.

25:08.680 --> 25:10.680
An art festival was also held there.

25:11.400 --> 25:12.480
Yeah, I'm fine.

25:14.320 --> 25:16.200
I shouldn't have let you eat all the Jiaoziba.

25:16.200 --> 25:17.480
I was just greedy

25:17.480 --> 25:18.800
and ate two breakfasts.

25:18.800 --> 25:20.130
You should have told me.

25:20.280 --> 25:20.960
What?

25:21.640 --> 25:23.240
Your thoughts and feelings,

25:23.480 --> 25:24.540
you can let me know.

25:24.960 --> 25:26.490
Chopping wood is possible.

25:26.520 --> 25:28.200
Ancient kilns used to be wood-fired.

25:28.200 --> 25:29.440
Everyone should eat more at noon.
